Package com.steelypip.powerups.jinxml

Interface EventHandler

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Builder
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConstructingEventHandler, EventInterceptor, StdBuilder
    public interface EventHandler
    This is the basic interface for incremental processing of an Element, especially construction. The expectation is that the handler-methods will be invoked in the order of an in-order traversal of the Element when viewed as a tree.
